ORG: ORGANIZATION - Companies, agencies, institutions e.g. Jyske Bank, Georgia-Pacific Corp.
PERS: PERSON - (including fictional) Eddy Bonte, President Obama
EVENT: EVENT - Named hurricane, sport event etc.
NAMIT: NAMED ITEM, titles of books, songs, works of art, products etc.
GPE: GPE - Countries cities, states - South East Asia, Midlothian
LOC: LOCATION not included in GPE - e.g. streetname, Murray River, Mount Everest
IDNUM: ID NUMBER - Passport number, CPR, reg. nr., phonenumber etc.
NUM: NUMBER - Number that does not fall into another type
WEB: WEBSITE - e.g. dr.dk, minhjemmeside dot com
EMAIL: E-MAIL - e.g. eksempel@gmail.com, Charlie (at) live dot com
PTITLE: PERSONAL TITLE - e.g. Mr. Mrs. Professor etc.
EIsC: Especially identifiable characteristics, tattoos, hair color, composure etc.
